<h3>Editing User Permissions</h3>
<hr />
<p>
In order to edit permissions, you must be assigned as the administrator on the current project.<br>
The permission of the current user, as well as the 'admin' user can not be edited.<br>
<ul>
	<li>To edit permissions, select the &quote;Edit Permissions&quote; from the main Requirments Manager view.</li>
	<li>Next to the user whose permission you desire to change, select the row that contains the name of the desired user.</li>
	<li>After selecting the row, click on the right side of the table to open a drop down menu of the available</li>
	<li>Select the new permission for the user.  Changes are saved automatically.</li>
	</ul>